THE JBay Animal Rescue Sanctuary will host a 2km Dog Walk at the Wild Fig Farm in Jeffreys Bay at 10:00 on October 22. Apart from the walk, there will be prizes for the ugliest dog, the most well-behaved dog, and for the most owner-dog look-alike. All dogs must be on a lead. The entrance fee is R50 per dog and a bag of dog food. For more information, contact Jessica Naud√© at 083 650 6373. 